{
  "stem": "11144.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when-- when they came in, which was not-- not too long after the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All I remember that my uncle, who was with us-- the one, the furrier-- he got the job with the Germans in-- in the German factory or whatever.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because he was making furs, he knew how to-- to sew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At that time, he became just a, you know, furrier, not a businessman.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I guess the Germans-- it was very cold there so they needed fur coats and whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he was working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They gave him a job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was working in one of the factories, so, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there wasn't paid labor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe they gave them-- maybe they gave them a soup, you know, soup for that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and-- and I remember that they were taking us-- and me, I was what, at that time, maybe 1941, I was 10 years old-- we had to go on the street and pick cigarette butts.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had to-- to pull grass from in between the stones, like, they had the sidewalk, and there was, like, grass growing in between.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the-- the-- the small children had to go and, you know, pick the thing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And once, I remember, I was taken to a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I guess it was a-- a German kitchen for-- for the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I guess we had to peel potatoes and scrub pots and wash dishes and-- and things like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I guess they-- they-- it is possible, now I'm not 100% sure, but it's possible that somebody from the Judenrate, you know, I-- I mean, that the Germans asked the Judenrate to deliver so many children or so many people or whatever.",
      "word_count": 42
    }
  ],
